title: About
text: jhollist consulting is a new consulting effort started by Jeff Hollister. Our focus is on supporting research, data, and analysis needs for client. Our expertise is in ecological and environmental research, but also adhere to the idea that “data is data.” Please reach out if you are interested in our services: jeff@jhollist.com
